longBusinessSummary: windeln.de SE, together with its subsidiaries, operates as an online retailer of baby, toddler, and children products in Germany, China, and other European countries. The company offers diapers, baby nutrition and drugstore products, strollers, car seats, clothes, toys, prams, children furniture, and safety products. It operates online shops under the windeln.de, windeln.com.ch, windeln.ch, bebitus.com, bebitus.pt, and bebitus.fr. The company also operates a retail shop in Germany. windeln.de SE was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Munich, Germany.
